Micheal John Duffy pleaded not guilty to murdering Colleen Deborah Ayers in 2012 . 
  Duffy claimed his former lover Rachel Evans was the one with a 'twisted desire to kill' Ms Ayers was strangled with a belt and buried in a shallow grave on her parent's property . 
  Evans has pleaded guilty to murder and will receive a reduced sentence for giving evidence at Duffy's trial . 
  Duffy told the court he only helped bury the victim's body . 
  The 33-year-old was murdered on her parents property in Picton . 
  Her decomposed body was found on the property in May 2012 . 
 